title: Week 15 recap
itunes:title: Week 15 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler – break down all the Week 15 action including the Cardinals clinching their first NFC West division title since 2009 with a win over the Eagles, and the Panthers outlasting the Giants 38-35 to hang on to their undefeated record. Plus, Browns tight end Gary Barnidge speaks up about his true origins, and Dan’s British accent.
